[[File:Jedi_ready.jpg|thumb|250px|right|The Jedi ready stance]]
Of all the ready stances in [[Lightsaber combat/Legends|Lightsaber combat]], the most common was '''Jedi ready'''. This involved placing the dominant foot back, with the blade in parry position on the dominant side.

